member.example:
This shows how to call this function.

var allLines = Prime.Services.FileService.ReadAllLines(@"~HDMT_TP_PATH\input_file");
foreach (var line : allLines)
{
    Prime.Services.Console.Print(line);
}

This shows how to call this function.

var fileContent = Prime.Services.FileService.ReadFile(@"~HDMT_TP_PATH\input_file");
foreach (var line : fileContent.split("\n"))
{
    Prime.Services.Console.Print(line);
}
